              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Only policy-violating reviews — fake, spam, off-topic, or offensive — can be flagged for removal via Google's reporting process. Legitimate negative reviews remain permanently. The most effective response is generating enough positive reviews to dilute their weight.</p></div></div>
          </div>
